柴狗都唔走去拍電影啦</blockquote><br />\n生化壽司冇睇?</blockquote><br />\n風雲冇睇？做埋3D舞台劇添<br />\n <br />\nBetween，我覺得外國拍劇都搵到好多錢，所以好多人可專注一個市場，唔洗好似香港咁，永遠都要3線歌影視發展，歌手又走去拍戲，拍戲又走去拍劇。雖然有時都有歌星Rihanna之類都會去拍下戲，拍劇嘅又會做好多電影配角，拍戲都會拍劇，不過人地個身份會明顯啲，等於你唔會話Micheal Jackson拍過戲，你會話佢係電影明星咁解，但係香港，林峰，除左叫藝人咁大包圍，你會叫佢咩？"},{"pid":"9c10f6524b5ec40db6e2be1fc98e6abbb371ed2a","tid":228021,"uid":30874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近年電視劇budget高左反而好多拍戲既走左去電視 又做得起</blockquote><br />\n呢幾年真係好多當紅既影星返去電視界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全部都係唔紅先去拍電視搏反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Matthew McConaughey已經唔係喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0c036b9befa82ff05bdf743acc00f73d52af11","tid":228021,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeafd1fd3bdbd08cc59b066557afb6e32608b57e","tid":228021,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近年電視劇budget高左反而好多拍戲既走左去電視 又做得起</blockquote><br />\n呢幾年真係好多當紅既影星返去電視界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全部都係唔紅先去拍電視搏反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTom Hardy都走左去拍左套劇啦"},{"pid":"f5d7d192a0da374105e1e0a11d4c6009fbe16843","tid":228021,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近年電視劇budget高左反而好多拍戲既走左去電視 又做得起</blockquote><br />\n呢幾年真係好多當紅既影星返去電視界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全部都係唔紅先去拍電視搏反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTom Hardy都走左去拍左套劇啦</blockquote><br />\n重有the rock都有套baller<br />\n呢兩個夠唔夠紅"},{"pid":"c67e68e1c892cfdf306b386932bd713c83e07bb5","tid":228021,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你查下拍美劇點計錢就知點解了</blockquote><br />\n點計？<br />\n<br />\n同荷里活戲最高薪個班有冇得比下？"}]}